file_content.text: From darkness, waking. Hunting algorithms primed. To death!
Activating ocular enhancement. Better to see sweat and pain.
Analysis complete. Prey is afraid... weakening....
The meal struggles against its fate. Adjusting strategy to compensate.
I am Vigilant. You will be undone.
Analyzing... The great dark comes for you.
Enemy vital organs functioning at sixty percent capacity. What will the Czerka make of you?
Blood and flesh. Cast in metal. Made invulnerable.
Battle subroutines startup. The dawn blooding waits.
The Czerka do not know what they made.
My world was hunger. Now all is lines and numbers. The perfection of death.
To know is to defeat. Storing enemy tactics; beginning cross-references.
Light nourishes. Draws into this shell.
Rerouting power. Drinking down victory. Fearing nothing.
The red dark rising. Losing power. System shutdown....
